Package: pould
Title: Phased or Unphased Linkage Disequilibrium
Version: 0.10.5.9000
Authors@R: person("Steven", "Mack", email = "steven.mack@ucsf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computes the D', Wn, and conditional ALD measures pairs of genetic loci. Performs these LD calculations on phased genotype data recorded using GL String or columnar formats. Alternatively, generates Expectation-Maximization estimated haplotypes from phased data, or performs LD calculations on EM estimated haplotypes. Perfoms sign tests comparing LD values for phased and unphased datasets, and generates heat-maps for each LD measure. Described by Osoegawa et al. (2019a) <doi:10.1016/j.humimm.2019.01.010>, and Osoegawa et. al. (2019b) <doi:10.1016/j.humimm.2019.05.018>.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Imports: haplo.stats,gap,stats,utils,ggplot2,reshape2,BIGDAWG
